name: Rennek (V)
Lore: 'Nerf herder. Personally oversees the herding of Jabba''s nerfs. Scruffy-looking appearance conceals his expertise in unusual combat techniques.',
Text: 'May be stacked on I Know That Laugh from hand for 2 force. While stacked on I Know That Laugh, stack face-up and during any battle may draw destiny. If destiny < number of your aliens in battle, reduce a participating character''s forfeit to 0.',
